      <title>根据瑞士提案，瑞银面临更高的资本规定</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-10/ubs-faces-substantially-higher-capital-rules-under-swiss-proposals</link>
      <description><![CDATA[瑞士信贷银行倒闭后，瑞士政府倡导进行改革，瑞银集团面临着监管资本要求的“大幅”增加。]]></description>
